OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FAston Villa's Morgan Rogers has
OL,7,Fcompleted a move to Chelsea for a
OL,8,FBritish record fee of around #117
OL,9,Fmillion on a contract until 2033.
OL,11,FThe 23-year-old moved to Villa Park in
OL,12,FFebruary 2024 in a deal worth #8m,
OL,13,Frising to #15m from Middlesbrough.
OL,15,FRogers scored 21 goals in 85 league
OL,16,Fappearances for Unai Emery's men and
OL,17,Fscored the third goal in their UEFA
OL,18,FEuropa League victory over Freiburg on
OL,19,FMay 20th.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
