OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784825275
OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FHe was also part of England's team for
OL,7,Fthe 2026 World Cup, assisting for
OL,8,FAnthony Gordon's goal against
OL,9,FArgentina in the semi-final.
OL,11,FNow, after returning with his England
OL,12,Fteammates on Sunday via Birmingham
OL,13,FAirport, Rogers was then on his way to
OL,14,FLondon on Monday (July 20th) to
OL,15,Fundergo a medical with Chelsea.
OL,17,FSo, now the boy from Halesowen has
OL,18,Fmoved on, but what does this mean for
OL,19,FAston Villa?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
