PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784825275
OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FBut that wasn't the first time Villa
OL,7,Ffans were able to catch a glimpse of
OL,8,Ftheir new player, as he faced them in
OL,9,Fthe Europa League final while playing
OL,10,Ffor Freiburg.
OL,12,FThe 20-year-old was named the young
OL,13,Fplayer of the season in that
OL,14,Fcompetition, and it is hoped he can
OL,15,Fpick up where Rogers left off.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
