CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784825275
OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FHowever, Rogers is the second
OL,7,Fmidfielder to leave Villa Park this
OL,8,Fsummer after the club confirmed the
OL,9,Fdeparture of Belgian Youri Tielemans
OL,10,Fto Manchester United for #35 million
OL,11,Fon July 14th.
OL,13,FTielemans has spent the past three
OL,14,Fseasons with Villa, having moved from
OL,15,FLeicester City in 2019.
OL,17,FHe also scored the opening goal in the
OL,18,FEuropa League final, which was his
OL,19,Ffinal appearance and goal for Villa.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
