OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784825275
OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FMidfielder Amadou Onana suffered an
OL,7,Fanterior cruciate ligament injury on
OL,8,Fduty at the World Cup with Belgium.
OL,10,FPartial tears or ruptures of the ACL
OL,11,Ftypically lead to players being
OL,12,Funavailable for between six and nine
OL,13,Fmonths.
OL,15,FBut again, Unai Emery has already
OL,16,Fsecured another midfielder, as the
OL,17,Fclub confirmed the signature of
OL,18,FWolves' Joao Gomes in a deal
OL,19,Freportedly worth #38m.
OL,26,@zD@Ktp
