OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FMidfielder Gomes, 25, who has won 10
OL,7,Fcaps for his country, ends a three-and-
OL,8,Fa-half-year spell at Wolves, where he
OL,9,Fmade 130 appearances after signing
OL,10,Ffrom Flamengo in Brazil.
OL,12,FWolves technical director Matt Jackson
OL,13,Fsaid: "Joao deserves everything he
OL,14,Fgets from the game. He's the type of
OL,15,Fprofessional that coaches love and
OL,16,Fplayers love, so he will go on to be
OL,17,Fthe outstanding player that we know he
OL,18,Fis."
OL,26,@uD@GOUzD@DO]
