OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FWe are nearly a month away from the
OL,7,Fstart of the new Premier League
OL,8,Fseason, with Aston Villa heading to
OL,9,FBrighton & Hove Albion on Sunday 23rd
OL,10,FJuly.
OL,12,FIt seems likely that Aston Villa will
OL,13,Fbe looking to make more signings
OL,14,Fbefore then to improve on their 4th
OL,15,Fplace finish in the league, as well as
OL,16,Fhaving a strong campaign in the UEFA
OL,17,FChampions League.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
