OL,3,CWhat does Morgan Rogers' British
OL,4,Crecord transfer mean for Aston Villa?
OL,6,FAlso, if Unai Emery's side can pick up
OL,7,Fanother trophy in the new season, we
OL,8,Fcould see those scenes again that
OL,9,Fpainted Birmingham, claret and blue.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
